title: YOLOv11-LCDFS: Enhanced Smoking Detection With Low-light Enhancement
excerpt: This paper presents a novel approach for smoking detection in low-light conditions by combining YOLOv11 with a low-light enhancement preprocessing pipeline.
citation: Yan J, Zheng Z, Yang Z, Jiang H, Wang P, Kuang F, Zhang S. (2023). "YOLOv11-LCDFS: Enhanced Smoking Detection With Low-light Enhancement." IEEE Access (Revision Required).

title: Deep Learning Model for Survival Prediction of Localized Upper Tract Urothelial Carcinoma Based on Multi-Phase CT Images and Clinical Data
excerpt: A novel deep learning approach that combines multi-phase CT imaging with clinical variables to predict survival outcomes in patients with upper tract urothelial carcinoma.
citation: Zhu K, Lin B, Yan J, Zhu H, Chen W, Yao X, You F, Pan Y, Wang F, Xia P, Li Y, Chen L, Yu Z, Miao S, Gao X. (Submitted 2024). "Deep Learning Model for Survival Prediction of Localized Upper Tract Urothelial Carcinoma Based on Multi-Phase CT Images and Clinical Data." Journal of Clinical Oncology (Revision Required).
